meta.title: Elmo Throws Temper Tantrum At Dinner

ttsdata.text: Hey daddy, what's for dinner tonight?
We're having steak and mashed potatoes tonight Elmo. You will love it, it will make you a strong little monster if you eat it every day.
I don't want steak and eggs, I want por edge from Hoopers Store.
No Elmo, we are not having por edge tonight. We are having steak and eggs. Por edge is for bears anyway. Not monsters. Come on, eat yoour steak and eggs before they get cold.
I don't want your stinky steak and eggs. They smell like stinky diapers. I want por edge and that's final!
Elmo, sit your furry ass down now and eat your dinner. I am the boss of the house. You follow my orders!
You know what, curse your steak and eggs! This is what I think of your shit food!
Elmo, how dare you throw away your food toward the beautiful wall. Your mother worked real hard cooking that dinner. That's it, you will now be grounded.
Hey daddy, what are we doing in the bathroom?
As I said earlier, you will now be grounded. For ever. Sayanora Elmo. You always were the most annoying muppet ever.
Oh noo! Daddy, what are you doing?
Goodbye L moe, say hi to oscar the grouch in the sewers for me.
Wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah waah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah.
Oh my god, it's Elmo. That annoying little monster is finally dead.
Woo hoo. Yee hah. No more hearing, elmo this and elmo that.
I'm glad you watched that episode. Subscribe to mister lie o sea for more episodes if you enjoy watching grounded episodes.
Or else I'll ground your ass for 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 years. Now go, subscribe. What are you waiting for?
